    <item>
      <title>特鲁多称特朗普的关税措施旨在制造混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-s-tariff-whiplash-is-designed-to-sow-chaos-trudeau-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多表示，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普正试图在其贸易伙伴中制造不确定性，以使他们失去平衡并削弱他们在贸易谈判中的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-s-tariff-whiplash-is-designed-to-sow-chaos-trudeau-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:30:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨称欧盟正在制定全欧盟范围的电动汽车激励计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/scholz-says-eu-prepares-bloc-wide-purchase-premiums-for-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨周二表示，欧盟正在制定一项在欧盟范围内实施电动汽车购买激励措施的提案，以支持欧盟陷入困境的汽车制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/scholz-says-eu-prepares-bloc-wide-purchase-premiums-for-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:14:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普上任第一天，埃隆·马斯克巩固了他在华盛顿的权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/elon-musk-cements-his-power-in-washington-on-trump-s-first-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[“它开始了，”唐纳德·特朗普就任美国第 47 任总统后不久，埃隆·马斯克于周一晚上写道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/elon-musk-cements-his-power-in-washington-on-trump-s-first-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:02:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普承诺对墨西哥征收 25% 关税，导致比索下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-s-pledge-to-slap-25-tariffs-on-mexico-sinks-peso</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普誓言要征收高额关税后，墨西哥比索大幅下跌，交易员们再次担心墨西哥将在未来四年成为目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-s-pledge-to-slap-25-tariffs-on-mexico-sinks-peso</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 14:52:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>移民突袭威胁使芝加哥枢纽变成鬼城</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/threat-of-immigration-raids-turns-chicago-hub-into-ghost-town</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥第二繁忙的零售街通常是该市西南部遍布墨西哥餐馆和墨西哥杂货店的繁华地区。到周一下午，这里已变成一座空城。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/threat-of-immigration-raids-turns-chicago-hub-into-ghost-town</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 14:18:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谢因鲍姆称墨西哥必须对特朗普的命令保持冷静</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/mexico-must-keep-cool-head-on-trump-orders-sheinbaum-says-m66jyfvz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆呼吁墨西哥人关注唐纳德·特朗普关于移民和贸易的行政命令的细节，同时警告美国不要干涉墨西哥领土。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/mexico-must-keep-cool-head-on-trump-orders-sheinbaum-says-m66jyfvz</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 14:10:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列总参谋长因 10 月 7 日袭击失败辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/israel-s-chief-of-staff-resigns-over-oct-7-attack-failure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列高级将领及其加沙指挥官因未能阻止 2023 年哈马斯袭击并引发多线战争而辞职，这一举动可能会给总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡的政府带来更多压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/israel-s-chief-of-staff-resigns-over-oct-7-attack-failure</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 13:29:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度将从美国接回 18,000 名公民以安抚特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/india-set-to-take-back-18-000-citizens-from-us-to-placate-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府准备与唐纳德·特朗普政府合作，识别并接回所有非法居住在美国的印度公民，这是新德里方面愿意遵守新任美国总统的规定并避免贸易战的早期信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/india-set-to-take-back-18-000-citizens-from-us-to-placate-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 10:02:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普下令取消有利于电动汽车的政策和补贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-orders-end-to-electric-vehicle-mandate-subsidies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普下令其政府考虑取消有利于电动汽车的补贴和其他政策，此举奠定了可能减缓美国清洁汽车普及速度的举措基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-orders-end-to-electric-vehicle-mandate-subsidies</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 02:38:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普赦免 1500 多名美国国会骚乱被告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-says-he-s-pardoning-nearly-all-capitol-riot-defendants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普赦免了几乎所有因参与 2021 年 1 月 6 日袭击美国国会大厦而被定罪的人，并下令撤销所有未决案件的指控，兑现了他返回白宫数小时后备受争议的竞选承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-says-he-s-pardoning-nearly-all-capitol-riot-defendants</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 01:03:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
